The folder listing for this series has cross-references not only to other correspondents in this series, but also to folders with descriptive headings arranged by subject in Series III. Many letters and memoranda that are filed in Series III do not, however, have cross-references in the folder listing for Series I. The letters and memoranda in Series III that do not have cross-references in the folder listing for Series I fall mainly under three headings: routine communications by U.S. and foreign government officials; all communications by foreign government officials that are filed under the names of their countries; and requests for assistance in getting passports (which are filed chronologically in Series III, 
                     Passports
                  ).

